  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926400/extras/ebb1b7d19cf85c29f65de2cf987130c3.avif?t=1669142009\" width=624 height=164 /></span><br><strong>Scatteria</strong> is a 2D Platformer shooter with a big selection of different firearms and explosives. <br>Many different post-apocalypse levels to choose to fight your battles against your friends. Everything is destroyable with explosives. Scatteria has support for couch gaming with split screen mode. <br><br>or against waves of A.I in <strong>single player mode.</strong> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926400/extras/9b71bc6cb7ded674719c1f7a73c0a074.poster.avif?t=1669142009\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926400/extras/9b71bc6cb7ded674719c1f7a73c0a074.webm?t=1669142009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926400/extras/9b71bc6cb7ded674719c1f7a73c0a074.mp4?t=1669142009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Take cover in bunkers, basements, destroyed ruins, foxholes or behind sandbags. <br>Destroy the environment with explosives to make your enemies time harder! Or just explode them into smaller pieces.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926400/extras/a5ca679a447d4149c90c75c40a759486.poster.avif?t=1669142009\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926400/extras/a5ca679a447d4149c90c75c40a759486.webm?t=1669142009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926400/extras/a5ca679a447d4149c90c75c40a759486.mp4?t=1669142009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926400/extras/8e95004e9ce93928912487cf7f48c488.poster.avif?t=1669142009\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926400/extras/8e95004e9ce93928912487cf7f48c488.webm?t=1669142009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926400/extras/8e95004e9ce93928912487cf7f48c488.mp4?t=1669142009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Fluid 2d platformer controls</strong><br>Two players on keyboard<br>Or up to 4 with Controllers (Xbox + Playstation style controllers for Pc supported)<br></li><li><strong>Local Split screen up to 4 players</strong><br></li><li><strong>Lots of weapons to choose from: </strong>Including Pistol, Rifle, Submachine Gun, Shotgun, Grenade Launcher, Bazooka, Assault Rifle<br></li><li><strong>Destroyable environments! Nearly everything can be destroyed</strong><br></li><li><strong>And cool explosives</strong></li></ul><strong>What are you waiting for? The apocalypse is waiting for you!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926400/extras/2a8f1ba2b3457016437aa45e676d9ce9.poster.avif?t=1669142009\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926400/extras/2a8f1ba2b3457016437aa45e676d9ce9.webm?t=1669142009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926400/extras/2a8f1ba2b3457016437aa45e676d9ce9.mp4?t=1669142009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926400/extras/ebb1b7d19cf85c29f65de2cf987130c3.avif?t=1669142009\" width=624 height=164 /></span><br><strong>Scatteria</strong> is a 2D Platformer shooter with a big selection of different firearms and explosives. <br>Many different post-apocalypse levels to choose to fight your battles against your friends. Everything is destroyable with explosives. Scatteria has support for couch gaming with split screen mode. <br><br>or against waves of A.I in <strong>single player mode.</strong> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926400/extras/9b71bc6cb7ded674719c1f7a73c0a074.poster.avif?t=1669142009\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926400/extras/9b71bc6cb7ded674719c1f7a73c0a074.webm?t=1669142009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926400/extras/9b71bc6cb7ded674719c1f7a73c0a074.mp4?t=1669142009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Take cover in bunkers, basements, destroyed ruins, foxholes or behind sandbags. <br>Destroy the environment with explosives to make your enemies time harder! Or just explode them into smaller pieces.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926400/extras/a5ca679a447d4149c90c75c40a759486.poster.avif?t=1669142009\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926400/extras/a5ca679a447d4149c90c75c40a759486.webm?t=1669142009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926400/extras/a5ca679a447d4149c90c75c40a759486.mp4?t=1669142009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926400/extras/8e95004e9ce93928912487cf7f48c488.poster.avif?t=1669142009\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926400/extras/8e95004e9ce93928912487cf7f48c488.webm?t=1669142009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926400/extras/8e95004e9ce93928912487cf7f48c488.mp4?t=1669142009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Fluid 2d platformer controls</strong><br>Two players on keyboard<br>Or up to 4 with Controllers (Xbox + Playstation style controllers for Pc supported)<br></li><li><strong>Local Split screen up to 4 players</strong><br></li><li><strong>Lots of weapons to choose from: </strong>Including Pistol, Rifle, Submachine Gun, Shotgun, Grenade Launcher, Bazooka, Assault Rifle<br></li><li><strong>Destroyable environments! Nearly everything can be destroyed</strong><br></li><li><strong>And cool explosives</strong></li></ul><strong>What are you waiting for? The apocalypse is waiting for you!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926400/extras/2a8f1ba2b3457016437aa45e676d9ce9.poster.avif?t=1669142009\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926400/extras/2a8f1ba2b3457016437aa45e676d9ce9.webm?t=1669142009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926400/extras/2a8f1ba2b3457016437aa45e676d9ce9.mp4?t=1669142009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>"